# Wokki frontend

Read [CLAUDE.md](../../CLAUDE.md), [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md), [.cursor/contexts/wokki.md](../contexts/wokki.md). Business rules: `../wokki-server/docs/business-rules.md` (`BR-xxx`). FE integration: `../wokki-server/docs/vi/fe-integration-guide.md`.

## Zones

- Business features only in `app/(app)/{admin|manager|user}/`
- Marketing: `app/(landing)/` · Auth: `app/(auth)/`
- New routes → update `components/app/app-nav.ts`

## Data layers

- `lib/api/services/fetchXxx.ts` — HTTP (no `lib/api/{domain}/` folders)
- `hooks/useXxx.ts` — TanStack Query (flat `hooks/`, not under `lib/`)
- `lib/support/{domain}/` — map-errors, assert-success, helpers
- `types/{domain}.ts` — DTOs
- Panels: `app/(app)/admin/{feature}/components/{Feature}Panel.tsx`

## Locale

- User-facing copy: **Vietnamese** (`html lang="vi"`, VND, `dayjs` vi)
- Keep established English UI terms: `Dashboard`, `Export CSV`, `Admin`, `Manager`, `Light`/`Dark`

## Business UX (must match backend)

- Schedule **preferences** advisory; official schedule = published **assignments**
- Preferences editable in **Draft** only; **Published** = view-only
- Auto-schedule: chi nhánh → phòng ban → tuần; branch `LocationSchedulingPolicy` required before suggest
- Bedrock: advisory insight only — scheduling must work when Bedrock unavailable
- `GET /auth/me` ≠ `GET /self/*`

## UI

- Tailwind v4 tokens in `app/globals.css`; brand blues from `@theme`
- Prefer `components/ui/` primitives; no CDN UI or raw design HTML

## Done gate

- `npm run type-check`; `npm run build` for structural changes
- Correct zone + Vietnamese copy + nav updated if new route
